  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains an orphan claim (W-EP-01): the central credibility claim references extensive supporting work in prose but carries no structured prov:wasDerivedFrom link to any Evidence node.",
