      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry and operating conditions must be the same FDA generic pump geometry at the same five COU operating points; no surrogate geometry extrapolation permitted at MRL-5.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry, which matches the COU geometry. However, two of the five COU operating points were not covered by available experimental data and were assessed by interpolation from adjacent validated points. Substantial gap."
    },
