      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of simulation setup by a second qualified analyst; documented checklist for boundary condition assignment and material property entry.",
      "rationale": "No independent second-analyst review was performed. Setup checklist was created post-hoc and not used during the original simulation campaign. Factor not formally assessed."
    },
    {
