      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal model form uncertainty quantification including comparison of at least two turbulence closure models and two hemolysis constitutive models with sensitivity analysis on QoI.",
      "rationale": "Only SST k-omega turbulence model was used; no alternative turbulence closure comparison was performed. Power-law hemolysis model was used exclusively without comparison to strain-based or energy dissipation models. Major epistemic gap at MRL-5."
    },
    {
