      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary condition inputs must have documented uncertainty distributions; Monte Carlo or equivalent UQ must propagate all input uncertainties to hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ (n=2000) was performed on five key input parameters (viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients, inlet flow rate, rotational speed). Three additional potentially influential inputs (outlet pressure waveform, wall roughness, red blood cell fragility index) were not included in the UQ. Partial compliance."
    },
